<view><view class="changePwd"><view class="changePwd-text">修改登陆密码，修改后下次登陆您需要用新密码登陆</view><view class="changePwd-old"><view class="changePwd-old-pwd">旧密码</view><view class="changePwd-old-input"><input style="{{'font-size:'+(system=='IOS'?'8px;':'20px')+';'}}" type="text" password="true" maxlength="15" placeholder="请输入旧密码" placeholder-class="placeholder_style" data-event-opts="{{[['blur',[['checkOld',['$event']]]],['input',[['__set_model',['','oldPwd','$event',[]]]]]]}}" value="{{oldPwd}}" bindblur="__e" bindinput="__e"/></view></view><view class="changePwd-new"><view class="changePwd-new-pwd">新密码</view><view class="changePwd-new-input"><input style="{{'font-size:'+(system=='IOS'?'8px;':'20px')+';'}}" type="text" password="true" maxlength="15" placeholder="请输入新密码" placeholder-class="placeholder_style" data-event-opts="{{[['blur',[['checkNew',['$event']]]],['input',[['__set_model',['','newPwd','$event',[]]]]]]}}" value="{{newPwd}}" bindblur="__e" bindinput="__e"/></view></view><view class="changePwd-comfire"><view class="changePwd-comfire-pwd">确认新密码</view><view class="changePwd-comfire-input"><input style="{{'font-size:'+(system=='IOS'?'8px;':'20px')+';'}}" type="text" password="true" maxlength="15" placeholder="请再次输入新密码" placeholder-class="placeholder_style" data-event-opts="{{[['blur',[['checkComfire',['$event']]]],['input',[['__set_model',['','comfirePwd','$event',[]]]]]]}}" value="{{comfirePwd}}" bindblur="__e" bindinput="__e"/></view></view><view class="changePwd-content">密码必须6~12个字符，而且同时包含字母和数字。</view><view data-event-opts="{{[['tap',[['submit',['$event']]]]]}}" class="changePwd-btn" bindtap="__e">确认修改</view></view></view>